Package: com.sinfool.ccadaptivedarkmodecustomiable
Name: CC - Adaptive Dark Mode (Customizable)
Author: Sinfool
Description: Gives the control center a dark style while using the current background to adaptively color the bubble background. Gives the control center a dark style while using the current background to adaptively color the bubble background.
 .
 I provided many customizable options i.e. blur, alpha, white overlay, saturation etc. along with some general suggestions as to what values to use but you can experiment with your own values.  I suggest changing only one unit at a time (& respringing) to check your results.
 .
 NOTE: This hasn't been tested with any other tweaks that change bubble colors etc. so you may need to disable them for this patch to work effectively.
 .
 P=pass-through,  D=Delete
 .
 [v.1] Tested with an iPad mini 4 10.2.  (3-22-17)
